data.description: Back on Market! Buyer got cold feet and now is your chance to make this one Yours!   New Price Reflects Sellers Motivation! You won't want to miss this one! Located in Popular Lakewood Estates neighborhood with a big yard and solid block construction! Large open living room welcomes you with all the light and brightness you desire. Meticulous home offers four bedrooms, three full baths. Two bedrooms located in the front of the home. One with ensuite bath and own private entrance. Perfect for home office or additional guests. Meeting in the middle, the large kitchen offers lots of granite countertop space and cabinets, s/s appliances. Off the kitchen you will enjoy additional living area to make a dining area or family room, you decide!  You will also find the third bedroom and owners master with walk in closet and ensuite bath. With over 1854 square feet of living space, this home is so much bigger than it looks from the street. Step inside and be amazed! Perfect floorplan for everyone to enjoy and have their own space. New sliding doors off the dining area and owner's master take you out to a paver patio deck to enjoy barbeque with your family and friends. Very private backyard space with crystal clear above ground pool to enjoy. Large yard space all around the home. Side entry under the carport for easy access into the home. Added extras include freshly painted exterior, sprinkler system in front yard, water softener. AC and Roof 7 years new! This beautiful home is move in ready and waiting for you! Call today for your own private showing.
